[1]: #series-graph.markArea.data.0.y
[2]: #series-graph.markArea.data.0.coord
[3]: #series-graph.markArea.data.0.type
[4]: #series-graph.markArea.data.0.valueIndex
[5]: #series-graph.markPoint.data.0.valueDim
[6]: https://echarts.apache.org/examples/zh/editor.html?c=scatter-weight

